                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/8631: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-04-11T12:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 11, 1927—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>141. Paragraph 4 of your No. 390, April 9, 1 p.m. You are given authorization to
                    act with your colleagues in the manner you suggested.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
